title: Unburdened
tooltip: universal property: creatures can fly freely here
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

While on a [[plane]] with this property, a creature can fly as easily as it can walk, unless it already can fly faster than it can walk, in which case its existing flight speed is enhanced.

See also [[Speed of Thought]].